{"type": "article", "id": 61733, "title": "这款推车，灵感源自设计师南美旅行时偶遇的鲣鸟｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-04T22:58:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 29871, "name": "Blå Station"}, {"id": 50885, "name": "Off-White™"}, {"id": 57045, "name": "不造 BUZAO"}, {"id": 57020, "name": "Lost&Found"}, {"id": 57046, "name": "Anki Gneib"}, {"id": 57047, "name": "Mia Cullin"}, {"id": 57048, "name": "Claes Carlsson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 85, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190304213015emoWI2RfBGV3b6yv.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Little Booby Trolley by Lost&amp;Found</h3><p>这是原创设计品牌失物招领 Lost&amp;Found 今年春季新品中的一款多功能家具，名为鲣鸟小推车。</p><p>“是边几，也是置物架。这个造型独特的小家伙儿，有着灵活多样的使用可能，它可以乖乖待在客厅沙发旁，也能在家庭工作区和你一起挥洒创意。”</p><p>在一次南美旅行中，设计师与鲣鸟相遇。浑圆的肚皮、大号的脚蹼，可爱模样瞬间击中所有人的萌点。旅行结束后，设计师将记忆画面再次提炼，深化成为小推车的雏形。</p><p>简洁流畅的侧面线条，极富动态美感。得益于被刻意放大的圆形车轮，需要时它可以自如移动。设计师从南美的自然景色中借取砂白与赭红两种颜色，赋予小推车两种不同性格：一个冷静温和，一个热情欢快。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213046JcsaTz234wkLh0OQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042130465AetphxPs7jI1lb8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213046NT9m0PtorBDGkIUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213047DJ6PKzmAgShWZCv5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213047VhFnQDLEprIuo3bJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.391000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213047sG3cej5lZEtkiv1p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.477000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>“HOT” series by BUZAO</h3><p>不造 BUZAO 是于 2017 年推出的一个实验性设计品牌，试图打破产品属性与艺术属性之间的定义，将艺术创作的不确定性引入产品设计当中，用设计手段与人产生关系。</p><p>今年春季，不造 BUZAO 将推出其积累两年的材料应用最新设计成果——“热 HOT”系列以及“空集 NULL SET 系列”。</p><p>“热 HOT”系列以电镀不锈钢为主要材质，包括边几、立柱、茶几和桌子，以及长凳。</p><p>剧烈迷幻的冷热撞色，不遗漏任一可见光的波段，色相在连续折面上像热象图解析呈现，镜面反射，形体纵横正立间增加色相交叠变化，与环境投射的光或影相互如实反馈。横竖重复的组合方式，常见于工地搭台、围板。极其炫丽浮夸的幻彩与粗鲁蛮横的形式形成反差，产生迷幻、跳脱、超现实的戏剧感受。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213141nhxFJvCEGMXP79Nr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213141Qu74robcUWwv2jMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042131416VkK7za3ZQEHxNgX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213142hYzD89s2HEMGWbSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042131423SZIUNWD0xiqL1Kr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213142Okjqsx2T0bY9wmut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213143clPgKG3V2orHF7pB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213143X0ch7AF39VqWiKSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.316667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213143M8dxcKVfLDPUh9lA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213141m19hOt5yYzXiq0Pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.buzao.me/\" rel=\"nofollow\">不造 BUZAO</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Denim Bottle Pouch by Off-White™</h3><p>不久前，Off-White™ 与法国天然矿泉水品牌 Evian 合作带来限量玻璃瓶身，最近，它们又带来一系列丹宁水瓶收纳袋 Denim Bottle Pouch。</p><p>这个系列有经过漂染的 White Denim 及 Black Denim 两款，肩带部分同样地以品牌最标志性的 Industrial Belt 构成，无论是袋身还是肩带等部分都分别印上不同的标示 Logo。<a href=\"https://www.ssense.com/en-cn/men/product/off-white/black-denim-bottle-pouch/3500839?ranMID=41610&amp;ranMID=41610&amp;ranEAID=9ieob0c66Uo&amp;ranEAID=9ieob0c66Uo&amp;ranSiteID=9ieob0c66Uo-08r.enGCSF3G7JadetUFaQ&amp;ranSiteID=9ieob0c66Uo-O2beAEkoLhk1Swcont_4bg&amp;utm_source=ls_APAC_9ieob0c66Uo&amp;utm_source=ls_APAC_9ieob0c66Uo&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=generic&amp;utm_campaign=generic&amp;utm_term=1&amp;utm_term=1&amp;siteID=9ieob0c66Uo-08r.enGCSF3G7JadetUFaQ&amp;siteID=9ieob0c66Uo-O2beAEkoLhk1Swcont_4bg\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042132490ES4yZI6LYpX5Cjc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042132499ot523WEgQyFiGjm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Avknoppningar by Anki Gneib &amp; Mia Cullin &amp; Nola &amp; Claes Carlsson </h3><p>这个名为 Avknoppningar 的项目近日在 2019 斯德哥尔摩设计周期间展出，项目由设计师 Anki Gneib 与 Mia Cullin、Nola 以及花卉布景设计师 Claes Carlsson 共同完成。</p><p>Anki Gneib 设计的“cacti”系列共包括三款作品，其中“cacti花架”的灵感来源于知名艺术家弗里达·卡罗在位于墨西哥的家中种植的仙人掌墙。“cacti cocoon”则利用标志性的曲线创造出一组悬挂式花篮，可以多个并列水平或垂直组合布置。“cacti bird”则是一款由流线型竖杆支撑的装饰性喂鸟器，还有可以悬挂在树枝上的悬挂版本可供用户自由选择。</p><p>Mia Cullin 的“gro”系列作品，目的是颂扬自然之美，将攀缘植物、藤蔓植物以及爬行植物引入到人造环境之中。</p><p>“gro 种植池”同样也经过设计者的更深入开发，创造出“gro 花瓶”。全新的种植池设有放射状框架，能够适合全部种类的花卉布置方式。一体式框架为植物茎秆、粗壮的绿叶以及小枝条提供支撑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213315h97akAdZN84st31J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213315x1K0JbXnScvu4ojB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213315veHCDy52cnoJZ7aQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213316o2BSxpNAPr3RlUsd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042133164r2IZtaFHBNDUgvO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213316kUoLCXQ1Vt78GJBe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213316TzZmupoIbQ4nDJk6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bob Home Sofa by Blå Station </h3><p>几年前，瑞典设计师 Stefan Borselius 和 Thomas Bernstrand 联手为瑞典家具品牌设计了一款名为 Bob 的座椅系统。去年，两人又推出了 Bob Job，重新定义了我们在开放式工作空间中的工作方式。</p><p>最近，它们进一步开发了这个系列，推出 Bob Home 沙发。这是一个舒适的模块化沙发系统，座位部分设计得更深，提供更柔软的缓冲作用，使其成为休息和放松时的完美沙发。</p><p>与旧款 Bob 沙发的设计一样，Bob Home 允许用户选择不同长度的直式沙发、转角沙发，甚至扶手椅，且有宽窄扶手两种选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042133567ryjhMzqE0ai9PIx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.568750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213356vbQ5ao1PXRCxlwMF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213356BgkI2bz8X0JqtEHD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903042133571JZOVNInXKQhoCtc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.778906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213357TX03ISouDxlBAhLP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.792354\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213357mVASD5CZbWlfvpXN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213357DdPAZvXzay5UhYlf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304213357ZHfDugkhVqTNKaOy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.791406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.blastation.com/products/product-families/bob-home/bob-home#&amp;tab=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blå Station</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}